data.description: Back on the market, buyer's financing fell through. This spectacular home situated on a large corner lot offers a well laid out floor plan which consists of 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, living room, dining room, den, office and a spacious kitchen with a walk-in pantry.  The beautiful granite countertops and sparkling hardwood floors will let you know you're in the right place. Sit and rock awhile on the large front porch. Addt'l xtras include a new roof & irrigation system. Plenty of equity to upgrade!
